Name: process_manager
Description: Process management tools.
Version: 1.0

Commands:
- proc_list (limit, name)
- proc_kill (pid)
- proc_start (command, cwd)
- proc_info (pid)
- proc_find (name)
- proc_suspend (pid)
- proc_resume (pid)
- proc_wait (pid, timeout)
- proc_run_capture (command, cwd, timeout)
